          "date": "2024-02-25 23:47:51.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Patrick Farrell",
          "email": "paf0187@gmail.com",
          "date": "2024-03-28 03:49:44.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-17433 osc: add dlmlock handling to DIO",
        "message": "LU-17433 osc: add dlmlock handling to DIO\n\nIn order to safely do parallel DIO with dlmlocks, we need\nto take and put a reference on the dlmlock used for each\nDIO.  With the new cl_dio_pages init and free code, this is\nstraightforward.\n\nWith this change, we can allow parallel DIO even when using\ndlmlocks.\n\nThis will also allow async hybrid writes.\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <patrick.farrell@oracle.com>\nChange-Id: I27b2d57e90178e0b9bbfd3942eec02ec74d3f022\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
